<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.6.8">
<l>maṟaṅkiḷarnta karuṅkaṭalnī ruranturantu parantēṟi yaṇṭattappāl</l>
<l>puṟaṅkiḷarnta kālattup poṉṉulaka mēḻiṉaiyu mūḻilvāṅki</l>
<l>yaṟaṅkiḷarnta tiruvayiṟṟi ṉakampaṭiyil vaittummai yuyyakkoṇṭa</l>
<l>niṟaṅkiḷarnta karuñcōti neṭuntakaiyai niṉaiyātār nīcartāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who do not contemplate the vast goodness</l>
<l rend="indent">of the dark splendor where luster rises</l>
<l>Which took you, placing [you] into the depths of his divine belly</l>
<l rend="indent">where virtue rose to save [you],</l>
<l>Taking in order the seven golden worlds</l>
<l rend="indent">at the time when the waters of the dark sea, where confusion rose,</l>
<l>Surging with force, spreading, ascending,</l>
<l rend="indent">rose outside the far edge of the firmament, are contemptible!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
